  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across 5 flow-speed combinations. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; required and achieved levels are recorded. Decision: Accepted. NOTE (adversarial): the ContextOfUse provides rich prose description of operating conditions but omits structured hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope links, leaving the model's bounded domain of valid use unspecified in machine-readable form (W-ON-02).",
